{"tid":1453351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回巢二哥劉業成極有可能只係condom","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:00:27.000Z","uid":38075,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d884da7f4eee1cae167a6d6697843389acb83867","tid":1453351,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"劉業成係回巢之前，同屬警隊一員，照道理如果佢係強硬派，又有咁精密嘅部署能力，應該早就跟住禿鷹上左位。<br />\n<br />\n但細心諗下，佢極有可能係比人搵返黎食死貓，然後鄧炳強名正言順上位，反正條友休都一早退左，返黎幫手頂一下又有安家費收。<br />\n<br />\n請大家記住唔好再比佢地轉移焦點，濫權係成個警隊都濫權，問責嘅係成個政府，甚至中共做成，唔好到時比佢地搵幾個人祭祈就收貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7f9c77211bc8d84fabcdd9d2bfd572372108d5","tid":1453351,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c575d063242b89bfb90b97195d405801ee8726a9","tid":1453351,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df956e24e2fbbd261747c521356f21762e32506","tid":1453351,"uid":60744,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:59:26.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n有機會畀隻死貓佢食再推返鄧炳強上去<br />\n<br />\n反正佢本身都退休，名譽唔太緊要<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得幕後都係鄧炳強，只係之前有spotlight對住佢先冇咁強硬"},{"pid":"ed2e986e30cf31ebe25f026112b3012ee2b5be54","tid":1453351,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"308990b45fa6b4a96999e4e2cf971b985f41b125","tid":1453351,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"要有幾咁唔怕死先會接呢個job, 天真到以為名譽受損咁簡單"},{"pid":"183cb49b86681a1ec5698ce5c65fead3b3e312c0","tid":1453351,"uid":254022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"事撚旦，黑警每件都平等，無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"aac00b5952422c692e677c7021113ab139cd0b57","tid":1453351,